game.name: Skull Racer
game.description:
Wow! The best racing game has come out! Where are you, gamers? We have tried to get you covered here with a brand new racing challenge where you have to control a monster truck to reach its destination. Once you get into this challenge, you cannot say no until you clear all the levels. Take your seat on your chosen vehicle and get ready to guide your chosen truck cross all the obstacles to reach your destination in Skull Racer!

Keep your eyes open all the time and try to grab as much coins as you can to boost your score in this HTML5 car game! Be fast and make sure that you reach your destination on time so that people call you a pro driver once again! The coins are scattered throughout the 20 levels. It will be your duty to get them without losing the balance of your vehicle. The top screen will show you how much distance will be there to be covered. 

Use the arrow keys or the control icons showed on the left and right bottom of the screen to operate your truck in this cool driving simulator! Turn your smartphones, tablets or iPhones or iPads into portrait mode to get the real driving fun in this addictive monster car online free game! This cool car driving simulator is playable in all the latest platforms without download and features easy controls for the gamers.
